text: The 1986 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1986 NCAA Division I-A football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by fifth-year head coach Gary Tranquill. ==Schedule== ==Personnel== ==References== Navy Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy Midshipmen football
